{"tid":1027780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲中大女生校園墮樓　自行報警求救","createTime":"2019-02-19T04:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T08:27:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a40d1ba1cc7f9e64e0bb61137d0e57e3b9ac20","tid":1027780,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"沙田中文大學女生企圖自殺。一名姓李(19歲)少女，今日(19日)凌晨4時許，由山村徑蒙民偉樓天台墮下，飛墮一層樓至對下平台，女生受傷仍然清醒，自行報警求助。消防員到場將她救下，交由救護車送院急救，現時情況穩定。警員在現場調查，相信事主於天台墮下，現場檢獲一封遺書，初步相信事主因生活問題及學業困擾，警方正聯同校方跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/bkn-20190219050505822-0219_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190219%2Fbkn-20190219050505822-0219_00822_001.html&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpErtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=efd914c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190219/bkn-20190219050505822-0219_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9a900f0864b1b7ad1709f575066bf4453afc351","tid":1027780,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49587432f7abaf601f6564b9f32333f4c424a8f","tid":1027780,"uid":139294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"睇完人生走馬燈就唔想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe6a63e956f91cc2be1f279a118340c33c1005d","tid":1027780,"uid":18999,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"自行報警求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff32227cb8639e24ecb4b5fe89a26c6e2906fd03","tid":10277